data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Chapel Hill! This meticulously maintained and completely renovated 3-bed, 2-bath all-brick ranch is a perfect blend of country charm and in-town convenience. Boasting privacy, coziness, and numerous updates, this home truly has it all.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a highly sought-after open floor plan flooded with natural light. The living room is a welcoming space featuring a wood-burning fireplace with built-ins, creating the perfect atmosphere for relaxation. The recently updated kitchen and baths showcase modern design and functionality, complemented by brand new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout.  The charm doesn't end there-discover the finished basement, a versatile space boasting professional paint, daylight windows, recessed lighting, and epoxy floors, providing the ideal setting for entertainment or a home office.  Car enthusiasts and hobbyists will appreciate the insulated 2-car attached garage and the oversized insulated 2-car detached garage with a workshop. With a concrete 3-car drive, including additional space for RV/boat storage, this property ensures you have room for all your vehicles and toys.  Step outside to the large privacy-fenced backyard, complete with a storage barn, a drive-thru gate, and a 31'x12' covered back patio with hot tub hookup-perfect for enjoying outdoor gatherings on nearly a half-acre of land adjacent to an immense school owned property.  The list of 2022-2023 updates is extensive, including kitchen, baths, flooring, new roof, furnace, AC, water heater, sump, exterior doors, and more. For a detailed overview, check out the attached Features & Updates Flyer.  Conveniently located next to Westlake Elementary, this home is nestled in a established neighborhood and offers easy access to schools, interstates, downtown, shopping, and more. With its unbeatable combination of features, this home is sure to go fast. Offering $5,000 in buyer's assistance for closing costs/down payment.
